<emphasis id="B70628C412526B4143ED5FF4EA05D1C8" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="40">Miconia machinazana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, fruiting branch, 
<emphasis id="1F329D21F0D969635D99AD359B6A30A1" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="40">Neill 16167</emphasis>
(photograph D.A. Neill).
</paragraph>
